.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Food: mango, tomato, grapes, cucumber, pear
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Birthday: march, april, september, january, december
Transport: van, quad-bike, snowmobile, car, ship
1. Nationality:british == Food:grapes
2. Nationality:swedish == Transport:snowmobile
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Food:tomato is on the left of Food:cucumber
5. Food:tomato == Beverage:coffee
6. Birthday:september == Transport:quad-bike
7. Food:pear == Birthday:april
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Birthday:december is on the left or right of Transport:van
11. Transport:ships is on the left or right of Birthday:april
12. Birthday:march == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Birthday:january
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Food:mango
15. Birthday:december is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
